    <h1>Propositions and reports to the Storting </h1>
  
  </div></div>
  

  <div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">   
  <div>
    <p>Propositions and reports to the Storting (St.meld.) are used when the Government asks the Storting to make a decision that is not related to an act. On this page you can find propositions to the Storting from the Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development.</p>
